EMAILPKT 1.4-stable (started 06.03.2003)

This file describe changes between EmailPkt 0.* and EmailPkt 1.4-stable

1. MAJOR feature improvements:

    - code a rewroted full
    - split into two programs: hesend & hereceive
    - drop "standalone" version
    - man page created
    - win32 build (in addition to unix)

2. CONFIG changes:
    - new token: sendmailcmd

3. IMPORTANT bugfixes:


